<p>Mazzeis <a id="TSJN-01-03-0438-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to letter in text" href="#TSJN-01-03-0438-ks-0001">letter</a> 7 was <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0350" class="document">dated 2 Mch. 1780, q.v.</a></p></div>
</div>
